title: Christmas In Europe 320cbr (Big Papi) 1989 Choir Orchestra Quart
description:
Source: 1989 CD
-
Note: This is the music to play all holiday and especially on Christmas morning. - Big Papi
-
By Mary 
For me it is not Christmas without this album.

In the evenings I sit looking at my Christmas tree in that magical daze with this timeless music.

The Children's choirs sing beautifully.

With breakfast on Christmas morning before everyone else is awake, this music is like pretty shimmering snow crystals,It transports me to alps and church and the heavens.. Lullabies of the Christmas Spirit.
